      "description": "The Defiance Daily Target 2X Long DRAM ETF (DRAL) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in information technology equity. The fund seeks daily investment results, before fees and expenses, of two times (200%) the daily percentage change in the share price of the Roundhill Memory ETF (Cboe BZX: DRAM). The Fund does not seek to achieve its stated investment objective for a period other than a single trading day. DRAL was launched on Jun 24, 2026 and is issued by Defiance.",
